 https://github.com/NadavTasher/Template/
-->
<html row lang="en">
<head>
    <!-- Charset -->
    <meta charset="UTF-8"/>

    <!-- App Description -->
    <meta name="description" content="easy. communicate. friends.">

    <!-- Viewport -->
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=5, user-scalable=yes, minimal-ui"/>

    <!-- Mobile -->
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#FFFFFF"/>
    <meta name="mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">

    <!-- Mobile Safari -->
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes"/>
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="Dweeder"/>
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent"/>

    <!-- Icons -->
    <link rel="icon"
          href="data:image/png;base64,"/>
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon"
          href="data:image/png;base64,"/>

    <!-- Repositories -->
    <meta name="repository-internal" content="modules/internal"/>
    <meta name="repository-external" content="modules/external"/>

    <!-- Stylesheets -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="template/template.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="application/application.css"/>

    <!-- Scripts  -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="template/template.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="application/application.js"></script>

    <!-- App Title -->
    <title>Dweeder | Easy communication</title>

    <!-- No Script -->
    <noscript></noscript>

    <!-- Additional -->
    <template id="dweed-expanded">
        <div style="margin: 1vh; /* background-color: ${color}; */" button column>
            <p huge left>${title}</p>
            <p small left>${contents}</p>
            <p tiny right>@${handle} at ${time}</p>
        </div>
    </template>
    <template id="dweed-normal">
        <div style="margin: 1vh;" onclick="window.location = '?dweed=${id}'" button column>
            <p small left>@${handle}: ${title}</p>
            <p tiny left>${contents}</p>
        </div>
    </template>
    <template id="dweed-compact">
        <a button tiny left href="?dweed=${id}">${title} - ${contents}</a>
    </template>
</head>
<body column>
<div id="setup" hidden>
    <!-- Title -->
    <p large left>Welcome to Dweeder</p>
    <!-- Input -->
    <p tiny left>Please enter your name (private)</p>
    <input small left id="setup-name" placeholder="Your name, e.g. Shuky Bonbon"/>
    <p tiny left>Please enter your handle (public)</p>
    <input small left id="setup-handle" placeholder="Your handle, e.g. @shuky"/>
    <!-- Button -->
    <button small center onclick="newUser()">Continue</button>
</div>
<div id="application">
    <div id="navigation" row>
        <img onclick="window.location = '/'"
             src="data:image/png;base64,"/>
        <p tiny center onclick="UI.view('compose');">Compose</p>
        <p tiny center onclick="UI.view('dweeds'); loadDweeds()">Feed</p>
        <p tiny center onclick="UI.view('dweeds'); loadMentions()">Mentions</p>
        <p tiny center onclick="window.localStorage.clear(); window.location.reload();">Logout</p>
    </div>
    <div id="contents" column>
        <div id="compose" hidden>
            <!-- Title -->
            <p large center>What's on your mind?</p>
            <!-- Inputs -->
            <p tiny left>Dweed contents:</p>
            <input id="write-title" small left placeholder="Title"/>
            <input id="write-contents" small left placeholder="Contents"/>
            <!-- Button -->
            <button small center onclick="writeDweed()">Send Dweed!</button>
        </div>
        <div id="dweeds">
            <p large center>Wow. such many dweeds.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
